   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Advising on and designing behaviour change communications around counter-trafficking in persons</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is implemented by Winrock International and its four core partners organizations &#x2013; BBC Media Action, Liberty Asia, Resonance and World Vision &#x2013; who have specialized technical expertise in the areas of behavior change communications, protection and private sector engagement. In addition, the project will partner with local civil society organizations to scale promising practices and promote holistic, needs-based, gender- culturally-sensitive services for at-risk groups and survivors of human trafficking</narrative>
